N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 348.1 - Application

State Regulations

The fee schedule applicable to chiropractic services shall
be the chiropractic fee schedule in effect on the date on which the
chiropractic services were rendered, regardless of the date of
accident. Notes
